I SWEAR THATS WILLOW.jpg.lore: After about 1 week after this class trip. I temporarily moved to a new house, only reason for this was because the home owners were going on vacation for a while, and wanted us to take care of their cat. Said cat looks a lot like this cat.

Street.jpg.title: Not even close
Street.jpg.lore: "Not even close" I remember the place where i took this photo, we were going through a little passage, where it was very easy to fall down. When i took this photo I stumbled on something and I almost fell down. Anything for the memory.
